    "prompt": "<div><div class=\"stimulus_reference\"><div class=\"passage\"><div class=\"prose style:1\"><div class=\"standalone_image\"><img alt=\"Two figures are shown. Each figure shows three skaters on a frozen pond. In Figure 1, Skater A is at rest while Skaters B and C are holding hands and moving together to the right. In Figure 2, Skater A is at rest and Skater C pushes off of Skater B as they separate and both move to the right.\" src=\"/images/c21786168150469556f505ce0e71c6a5.svg\"></div></div></div></div></div><p class=\"stem_paragraph\">Three skaters are on a frozen pond. Initially, Skater <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"A\"><math alttext=\"A\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mtext>A</mtext></math></span></span> is at rest and Skaters <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"B\"><math alttext=\"B\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mtext>B</mtext></math></span></span> and <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"C\"><math alttext=\"C\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mtext>C</mtext></math></span></span> are holding hands moving together to the right, as shown in Figure <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"1\"><math alttext=\"1\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>1</mn></math></span></span>. Skater <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"C\"><math alttext=\"C\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mtext>C</mtext></math></span></span> then pushes off of Skater <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"B\"><math alttext=\"B\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mtext>B</mtext></math></span></span> and they both continue moving to the right, but Skater <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"C\"><math alttext=\"C\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mtext>C</mtext></math></span></span> moves away from Skater <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"B\"><math alttext=\"B\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mtext>B</mt